Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.52,0:00:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you do, Ein?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.36,0:00:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I say ex-Phantom?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.32,0:00:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.41,0:00:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am... Phantom now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.38,0:00:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scythe calls me Drei.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.13,0:00:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ein, Zwei, Drei...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.47,0:00:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have to explain, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.64,0:00:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Greeting people with "How do you do"? How lovable Phantom has become.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.27,0:00:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I just wanted to kill you, I could have done it any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.07,0:00:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that wouldn't be fun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.99,0:01:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Locating you and driving you into a corner, then killing you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.24,0:01:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've lived the past two years looking forward to just doing that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.16,0:01:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while being the property of that damn Inferno.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I'll have fun as much as possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.25,0:01:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,watching you run in fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.99,0:01:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will that satisfy you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.43,0:01:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.97,0:01:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji looked so shocked when he saw me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.73,0:01:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He became pale, like he saw a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.31,0:01:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What shall I do next? I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.23,0:01:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't I kill you in front of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.28,0:01:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you think he'll react?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.91,0:01:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.12,0:01:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, you ran into me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.08,0:01:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be... killed here...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.42,0:01:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You're prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.31,0:02:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You risk your life to protect Reiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How commendable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you who is commendable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.90,0:02:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't forget the fact that Reiji abandoned you all this time, could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.83,0:02:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wish he'd regret it more.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wish he'd feel sadder.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.37,0:02:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's no longer the Reiji you knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He put the past behind him and lives in the present.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.09,0:02:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.34,0:02:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're only a ghost from the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.68,0:02:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you stand in his way,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.10,0:02:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he will... shoot you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You talk like you know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.19,0:02:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.19,0:02:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,his real strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.11,0:03:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes the hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elen... Cal...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason for you two to kill each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear what he said?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ein... sounds like you had the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.47,0:03:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet. All the actors aren't assembled yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and shoot... Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop it, Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.40,0:03:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You abandoned me once.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once... twice... it makes no difference, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.25,0:03:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot! But... I'll take her down with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take her to hell with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.48,0:04:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... this is just what I was afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you acting so impulsively?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.95,0:04:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in Japan, you dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think that you can get away with firing a gun in the middle of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Then shoot... Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when you do
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll shoot everyone down
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,including you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, you first, Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put down your gun and beat it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:05:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got my gun pointed at those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, what a boring ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's your successor, Zwei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm assigned to support her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to that, I feel more dead than alive these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for looking after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.77,0:05:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, you're done playing students.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The organization has found out your whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and get out of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, sorry to say this, but I'm not sure if I can continue to stop that mad dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. We'll hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.08,0:05:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lizzie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.83,0:06:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really... uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Live in the present, Zwei...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Live the life Clo couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you going to shoot?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.63,0:06:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She and I... If you had to choose one of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.94,0:06:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll secure an escape route.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During that time, we'll have Inferno restrain Drei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time to use our trump card has finally come.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go without you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a phone call, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.11,0:07:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... he said he's Claudia's right hand man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiga speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been two years, Toru Shiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just who I said I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.26,0:07:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.47,0:07:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Claudia McCunnen's right hand man?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Asian brat who was always by her side...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember correctly, he was an assassin called...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you're under pursuit by the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know Shinokura Academy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinokura...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Kaiten Godo's... the Godo Family's head's daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.45,0:08:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio Fujieda, goes to that school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you do understand, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you're talking about is off-limits!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. As long as nothing happens to us, we won't harm Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as nothing happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inferno's assassin is after me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.77,0:08:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop her, Toru Shiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.89,0:08:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put a collar on Inferno in Japan using your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether you do it or not is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do everything possible, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've become a good actor, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.84,0:08:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not as good as you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If things go well, we can buy some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.92,0:08:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiga is smart. It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:09:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he'll do as we hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.56,0:09:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if it doesn't work?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.89,0:09:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, we'll come up with another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't intend to put Mio in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drei...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you happy that she's alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.37,0:09:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought she died on that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought because of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because I dragged her, a bystander, into my business, she died.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... she was alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll head north at dawn tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a smuggler cargo boat. I'll go negotiate in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.93,0:09:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. You stay by Mio's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.98,0:09:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotten late. I'll make dinner quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Phantom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from the senior members earlier and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.25,0:10:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like she has heard already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The daughter of Kaiten Godo, the Godfather of the Godo Family,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whose existence has been kept secret from the public...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.13,0:10:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like Zwei and Ein didn't disguise themselves as students just for fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who gives a damn about the Japanese mafia!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool down, Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Godo Family is also a respectable member of Inferno.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.57,0:10:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right. Your hands are tied until the safety of Godo's princess is secured.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.16,0:10:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zwei outwitted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it for this time. Wait for the next opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guarding a high school girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:10:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:11:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.05,0:11:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's an important person to me as well as to our Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you need us for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.43,0:11:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.89,0:11:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do all you can to protect her, even at the cost of your lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.57,0:11:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you detest him that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.99,0:11:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think I've been doing as I'm told by this damn organization?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.66,0:11:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so that I could hunt down and kill that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.67,0:11:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.17,0:11:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't bear to see you and Zwei kill each other, Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.18,0:11:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, you don't have confidence in me, do you. You think I'd lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.02,0:11:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that he deceived many people and made a fool of them two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.41,0:12:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was deceived, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's quite the con artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.74,0:12:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, when it comes to your case, Zwei was protecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He deceived me all that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.01,0:12:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't tell me anything and lied repeatedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was afraid of... the moment that he couldn't fool me any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.39,0:12:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason why he lied... was to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.98,0:12:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was only one thing that he wanted to protect...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.28,0:12:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He abandoned me after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He ran off with a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:13:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was no reason for you to become an assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.54,0:13:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you wanted to become one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm Phantom, who can scare even a crying child into silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.22,0:13:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even those gangsters who used to do whatever they wanted in town
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.27,0:13:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,get terrified just by hearing my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.77,0:13:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's great, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kicking those guys around, making fun of them and killing them...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.78,0:13:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any other life that's this fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was afraid of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I was going to be too strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.75,0:13:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He deceived and used me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make him pay for that dearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:14:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal... You're like a firework that burns itself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.98,0:14:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that Elen is absent today?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.19,0:14:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she came down with a bit of a fever last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.87,0:14:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's just a cold, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have told me sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would've gone to your place and took that cold from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Hey! Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you idiots are having a dumb conversation as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, we're all going to see a movie, so I'll let you guys come too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.63,0:14:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you call an invitation?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.72,0:14:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph! Mio is coming, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.14,0:14:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh... Sorry, I'll pass today. I've got something to do today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.89,0:14:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.77,0:14:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, a good guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.06,0:14:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, we were both tricked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.57,0:14:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That darn Sanae. "All going to see a movie"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.74,0:14:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a roundabout way of doing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.62,0:15:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope Elen feels better soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.26,0:15:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go see a movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.14,0:15:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I go home, I'll just interrupt Elen's sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.77,0:15:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm doing things with Mio Fujieda like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.44,0:15:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it'll put pressure on Shiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.46,0:15:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got carried away like a kid. I'm embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The movie was quite interesting, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to admit, I appreciate Sanae.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.14,0:16:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you are a little mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I say...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.77,0:16:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel that how you see things is different from ordinary people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyday life is just natural and trivial to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I feel like you really cherish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.33,0:16:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So when I look at you I come to like where I am right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.84,0:16:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if things are boring and you get tired of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they all mean something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel that everyone might just be forgetting that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I interrupting?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.45,0:17:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... so that girl is Mio Fujieda, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.54,0:17:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ein, me and Godo's daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.71,0:17:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure do use all the women who get close to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you don't really intend to do anything to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.22,0:17:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's resume the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.39,0:17:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's settle who the real Phantom is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are Phantom, Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.86,0:17:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a student now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh, Zwei. You aren't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.69,0:17:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want my head, I'll give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.85,0:17:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... have you continued to run up until today?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.54,0:17:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.63,0:17:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just wanted to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.72,0:17:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I not right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm killed by your hands, that's just what I deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been doing things that I deserve to die for.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.06,0:18:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have a condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In return for my life, I want you to let Elen... let Ein go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.24,0:18:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you want to sacrifice yourself for that woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.08,0:18:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll no longer be a problem for Scythe or Inferno.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to protect her even if it kills you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.25,0:18:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You abandoned me and ran off by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet you have someone that you have such feelings for, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.18,0:18:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true, Cal. At the time, I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.90,0:18:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.73,0:19:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But first I'll hurt you more... and make you suffer more...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.58,0:19:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't shoot in this situation, you're a real softy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.02,0:20:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you dying here would be just natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.24,0:20:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
